urce: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 6652 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35309,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/02\/27\/parable-dunya\/","url_meta":{"origin":17095,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Dunya: Worldly life is like good food becoming excrement","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 27, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Dahhak ibn Sufyan reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said to him, \u201cO Dahhak, what are you eating?\u201d He said, \u201cMeat and milk.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cThen what will it become?\u201d He said, \u201cYou know what it will become.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cVerily, Allah Almighty\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":9675,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/11\/02\/health-food-faith-dunya\/","url_meta":{"origin":17095,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Life: Whoever is healthy, safe, faithful has everything","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 2, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"'Ubaydullah ibn Mihsan reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever among you wakes up secure in his property, healthy in his body, and he has his food for the day, it is as if he were given the entire world.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2346\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0